            <section ID="L48a427a0-6154-4253-8d57-644a663118f6">
               <id root="1c64b97a-f5b7-4431-9b79-a1900e84dc8d"/>
               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <title>Directions </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Brush and floss your teeth to remove plaque. Adults and children 6 years of age or older: Add one drop of FluoriShield into each tooth area in the custom carrier and spread evenly with the applicator tip of the fluoride bottle. Place carriers over the teeth and let it remain in place for one (1) minute or longer (as directed by your doctor). Expectorate the excess gel. Clean carriers with cold water. Spit out the excess gel in the mouth and do not rinse, eat, or drink for thirty (30) minutes.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20181213"/>
            </section>
